						               													<description>Cyntopia: The future is nowis a cooperative, fast-paced and action packed tabletop boardgame which takes places  in a dystopic future. You'll fight huge corporations as an Edgewalker and make your living while flirting with the line. Will you fight or fall?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cyntopia: The future is now is now takes place in a completely new cyberpunk universe. It features a cooperative gamemode for 1-7 players, a modular boardgame, over 30 miniatures and a random mission system.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to fulfill your mission as Edgewalker, the mission and corporation you work against will be drawn by cards and decide the first floortile of the boardgame.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the Edgewalk you have to fight against the guards of the corporation in a simple, yet luck and strategy based fighting system. The success of each interaction depends on the dice roll.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
